@Node "DLDConfig_History" "Program history for DLDConfig."

V1.0	-First working version.

@Endnode

@Node "DLDConfig_HowToInstall" "How to Install DLDConfig."

How to Install DLDConfig.

 -Just copy DLDConfig to any directory.

@Endnode

@Node "DLDConfig_HowToUse" "How to use DLDConfig."

How to use DLDConfig.

This program is used to generate a small configuration-file. This file
contains the same options as you can specify in the template.
Instead of typing all the options in the template you just execute
DLDConfig, set the options, click the "save" gadget and enter a filename.
When executing DLDCheck you just enter this in the shell.

DLDCheck mode c name <Archivename> Configfile <Configfilename>

DLDCheck will now load the options from <Configfilename> and carry on
with these options.

@EndNode
